<font color="#FF0000">SOCKS AND MONSOON RAINS</font><br>
<tt>Thu Oct 23 18:56:10 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I like the colors we saw in Vietnam,<br>
Green, orange, red, purple, black, Grey, Blue and little shades of varying flesh tones all on the bottom of my feet just before the corpsmen medivacked me out at the end of operation Foster.<br>
The medics at Chu Lai, had all the big honchos come around and they took pictures of my feet on account they had never seen anything quite like it before. <br>
I still cannot walk barefooted on grass without the bottom of my feet breaking out like fine sliced bread.
